---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
 title="Privacy Policy | Pizza & Friends"
 description="How joinpizza.fun handles visitor data and third-party services."
>
 <main id="main-content" class="legal-page">
 <a href="/" class="legal-back">&larr; Home</a>

 <header class="legal-header">
 <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
 <p class="legal-lede">
 Last updated: July 4, 2026. Pizza &amp; Friends (joinpizza.fun) is a community
 landing page for meetups and side projects. It is <strong>not</strong> a corporate
 product or official university service.
 </p>
 </header>

 <article class="legal-body">
 <section>
 <h2>What this site is</h2>
 <p>
 This is a static community site with photos, event highlights, and links to our
 Discord and social channels. There are no user accounts or sign-up forms on this
 website.
 </p>
 </section>

 <section>
 <h2>Information we may process</h2>
 <ul>
 <li>
 <strong>Hosting logs.</strong> Vercel (or similar hosting) may log standard request
 metadata such as IP address, browser type, and timestamps for reliability and security.
 </li>
 <li>
 <strong>Analytics.</strong> We may enable privacy-focused web analytics (for example
 Vercel Analytics) to understand traffic patterns. We do not intentionally collect
 names or contact details through analytics.
 </li>
 <li>
 <strong>Email contact.</strong> If you email organizers directly, your message is
 handled through your email provider and ours: not through this website.
 </li>
 </ul>
 </section>

 <section>
 <h2>Community photos</h2>
 <p>
 The site displays photos and videos from community events. If you believe your image
 should be removed, contact the organizers listed on the homepage.
 </p>
 </section>

 <section>
 <h2>Third-party services</h2>
 <p>
 Links to Discord, Instagram, Facebook, LinkedIn, and other platforms are governed by
 those services' own privacy policies. Leaving this site means their rules apply.
 </p>
 </section>

 <section>
 <h2>Contact</h2>
 <p>
 Privacy questions? Email
 <a href="mailto:johnyumul.ph@gmail.com">John</a> or
 <a href="mailto:semariquit@gmail.com">Simonee</a>.
 </p>
 </section>
 </article>
 </main>
</Layout>

<style>
.legal-page {
 max-width: 40rem;
 margin: 0 auto;
 padding: 3rem 1.5rem 5rem;
 }

.legal-back {
 font-family: var(--font-geist-sans);
 font-size: 0.85rem;
 color: var(--text-muted, #6b6560);
 text-decoration: none;
 }

.legal-back:hover {
 text-decoration: underline;
 }

.legal-header {
 margin: 2rem 0;
 }

.legal-header h1 {
 font-family: var(--font-libre-baskerville);
 font-size: clamp(1.75rem, 4vw, 2.25rem);
 margin: 0 0 1rem;
 }

.legal-lede {
 font-family: var(--font-geist-sans);
 line-height: 1.65;
 color: var(--text-muted, #6b6560);
 margin: 0;
 }

.legal-body section {
 margin-bottom: 1.75rem;
 }

.legal-body h2 {
 font-family: var(--font-libre-baskerville);
 font-size: 1.1rem;
 margin: 0 0 0.5rem;
 }

.legal-body p,
.legal-body li {
 font-family: var(--font-geist-sans);
 line-height: 1.65;
 color: var(--text-muted, #6b6560);
 }

.legal-body ul {
 margin: 0.5rem 0 0;
 padding-left: 1.25rem;
 }

.legal-body a {
 color: inherit;
 }
</style>
